Women's t-shirt model (shirt-womens.glb)
========================================

This garment was supplied by the site owner (a textured photogrammetry scan,
provided as a ~9.2 MB / 25k-vertex Blender-exported glTF, replacing an earlier
scan). For the studio it was welded, had its textures and materials stripped
(the studio recolours garments at runtime), vertex normals recomputed, and was
re-centred and height-normalised, then re-exported as a compact binary glTF
(~0.8 MB).

ACTION REQUIRED: confirm the original source and licence of this scan and record
it here (author, URL, and licence terms). If the scan is under a licence that
requires attribution (e.g. CC-BY) or restricts commercial use, that must be
honoured before the site goes live.
